 <text id="F3006T">
  <front id="d2">
   <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
    <p>Demus is pleased to report that he is now the chief commissary clerk.</p>
   </div1>
  </front>

  <body id="d4">
   <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
    <head>
     <name type="recipient">Mary Jane Demus</name>
    </head>

    <opener>
     <dateline>
      <date value="1864-08-18"><orig reg="august">auges</orig> the 18th</date>
      <name type="place">morris<lb/> south <orig reg="carolina">carlina</orig> 54th <orig
       reg="headquarters">headqears</orig>
      </name>
     </dateline>
     <salute><orig reg="My">Miy</orig> Dear</salute>
    </opener>

    <p>i take this present <orig reg="time">tim</orig> to <orig reg="inform">in for</orig> you that
     i am Well at this present time and i hope <orig reg="When">Whean</orig>
     <orig reg="these">thes</orig> few lines reaches you <orig reg="they">tha</orig>
     <orig reg="may">ma</orig>
     <orig reg="find">finde</orig> you <orig reg="enjoying">in the Joine</orig> the <orig reg="same"
      >sam</orig> state of i <orig reg="receive">receave</orig>
     <orig reg="your">yor</orig> kind letter last month and i Was glad to <orig reg="hear">hir</orig>
     <orig reg="from">frum</orig> you and all the rest but i am sorry to say that i think it long
      <orig reg="between">betiean</orig> letters <orig reg="for">fer</orig> i <orig reg="haven't"
      >hant</orig> had one for <orig reg="some time">som tim</orig> i am <orig reg="Just">Jest</orig>
     <orig reg="Waiting">Waiten</orig> for the <orig reg="mail">male</orig> to <orig reg="Come">Cum</orig>
     <orig reg="for">fer</orig> i hope to <orig reg="your">yor</orig>
     <orig reg="likeness">likenss</orig> in it i Was glad to <orig reg="hear">hir</orig> to <orig
      reg="hear">hir</orig> that you got mine <orig reg="for">fer</orig> i sent John <orig reg="my"
      >mi</orig>
     <orig reg="likeness">likenss</orig> a long <orig reg="time">tim</orig> but i <orig reg="Don't"
      >Dont</orig>
     <orig reg="know">now</orig>
     <orig reg="Whether">Wether</orig> he got it or not but i am happy to say that i have got a good
     place now i am in the <orig reg="chief">cheaf</orig>
     <orig reg="commissary">comesarry</orig>
     <orig reg="Clerk">Clirk</orig> and i <unclear>mes</unclear> With the <unclear>offrs</unclear> i
     live at the <orig reg="top">to</orig> of the <unclear>pile</unclear> times is good <orig
      reg="here">hear</orig> now i have not got <orig reg="time">tim</orig> to <orig reg="write"
     >rit</orig> much this time but i Will <orig reg="write">rit</orig> in the <orig reg="next"
     >nex</orig> letter all <orig reg="about">a but</orig></p>

    <p>Direct <orig reg="your">yor</orig> letter to Morris <orig reg="island">iland</orig> south
      <orig reg="carolina">carlina</orig><lb/> Camp 54th<lb/>
     <abbr expan="Company">Comy</abbr>k<lb/> David A Demus</p>

    <p><orig reg="Please">Pleas</orig> to <orig reg="write">rit</orig>
     <orig reg="soon">son</orig> nothing<lb/>
     <orig reg="more">mor</orig> at present</p>

    <p>But still <orig reg="remain">reman</orig></p>

    <closer>
     <salute><orig reg="your">yor</orig> Dear <orig reg="husband">husben</orig><lb/>you till <orig
       reg="Death">Deth</orig></salute>
     <signed>[David A. Demus]</signed>
     <seg type="postscript">
      <name type="recipient">Mrs Marry Jane Demus</name>
     </seg>
    </closer>
   </div1>
  </body>
